bsp;是正则表达式实例的只读属性。</p>\n<div id=\"sect2\">\n <table class=\"standard-table\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th class=\"header\" colspan=\"2\"><code>RegExp.prototype.ignoreCase</code> 属性的属性特性：</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>writable</td>\n      <td>false</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>enumerable</td>\n      <td>false</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>configurable</td>\n      <td>false</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"description","title":"描述","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>ignoreCase</code>&nbsp;的值是布尔对象，如果使用了\"<code>i</code>\" 标志，则返回 <code>true</code>；否则，返回&nbsp;<code>false</code>。\"<code>i</code>\" 标志意味着在字符串进行匹配时，应该忽略大小写。</p>\n<p>你无法直接更改此属性。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"example:_using_min_value","title":"例子：使用&nbsp;<code>ignoreCase</code>","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush:js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> regex <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">RegExp</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"foo\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"i\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>regex<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>ignoreCase<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// true</span>\n</code></pre></div>","titleAsText":"例子：使用 ignoreCase"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"规范","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>ECMAScript 3rd Edition. Implemented in JavaScript 1.2.</td>\n   <td>Standard</td>\n   <td>Initial definition.<br>\n    JavaScript 1.5: <code>ignoreCase</code> is a property of a <code>RegExp</code> instance, not the <code>RegExp</code> object.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/5.1/#sec-15.10.7.3\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 5.1 (ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">RegExp.prototype.ignoreCase</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Standard</span></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/6.0/#sec-get-regexp.prototype.ignorecase\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 2015 (6th Edition, ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">RegExp.prototype.ignoreCase</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Standard</span></td>\n   <td><code>ignoreCase</code> is now a prototype accessor property rather than an instance's own data property.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"javascript.builtins.RegExp.ignoreCase","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/RegExp/ignoreCase/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"相关链接","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/RegExp/global\"><code>RegExp.prototype.global</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/RegExp/lastIndex\"><code>RegExp.prototype.lastIndex</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/RegExp/multiline\"><code>RegExp.prototype.multiline</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/RegExp/source\"><code>RegExp.prototype.source</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/RegExp/sticky\"><code>RegExp.prototype.sticky</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"概述","id":"summary"},{"text":"描述","id":"description"},{"text":"示例","id":"examples"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"相关链接","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"ignoreCase 属性表明正则表达式是否使用了 \"i\" 标志。ignoreCase 是正则表达式实例的只读属性。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"RegExp.prototype.ignoreCase","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"RegExp.prototype.ignoreCase","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"RegExp.prototype.ignoreCase","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"RegExp.prototype.ignoreCase","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"RegExp.prototype.ignoreCase","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"RegExp.prototype.ignoreCase","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"RegExp.prototype.ignoreCase","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/regexp/ignorecase","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/regexp/ignorecase/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript","title":"JavaScript"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference","title":"JavaScript 参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects","title":"JavaScript 标准内置对象"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/RegExp","title":"RegExp(正则表达式)"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/RegExp/ignoreCase","title":"RegExp.prototype.ignoreCase"}],"pageTitle":"RegExp.prototype.ignoreCase - JavaScript | MDN","noIndexing":false}}